Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}最初的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我由于不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:09.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:24.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:29.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.16,0:00:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:37.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:44.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:47.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:50.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:55.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:59.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:05.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:10.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:21.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:27.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:32.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:38.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:43.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:45.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:48.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:52.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:55.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以护卫洛克贝尔小姐为幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央军派遣来的金普利的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想在这布里克斯干什么 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去北方的话就说一声呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常急的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们总是很急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 为什么进了牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是弄错了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会去办手续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 金普利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个家伙就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要相信金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个好人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克贝尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的双亲是在伊修瓦尔战死的医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回收遗体的是我的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚到了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶到现场的时候已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:02:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵循医道的伦理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最后都贯彻自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打心底敬佩他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望能在生前见到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常珍惜地带着和可爱的女儿一起拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是他们心灵的寄托吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够见到你是我的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉·洛克贝尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他在伊修瓦尔做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是从中尉口中听说过伊修瓦尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很喜欢温莉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想其他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要考虑其他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氢 氦 锂 铍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碳 氮 氧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱…爱德？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铝 硅 磷 铬 锰 铁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钴 镍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么偏偏喜欢上了这个奇怪家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了接神经的时候要说一声的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好轻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种强度不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 比起以前整体的强度下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各个重要地方都强化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么从牢里出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计这就是国家炼金术师的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在才换成冰寒地带专用的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是这家伙最合适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 轻战斗用机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M1910
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指甲强化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道材料用的是钻石？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 M1910·改 狂熊G
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德也装这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这位可爱的小姐是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的维护师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很恼火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到 北国专用机械铠 好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要看看我的工作室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看要看 我要看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为太过兴奋而到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要塞里面也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个很少见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鳄鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和父母很像 热衷于工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的特征是考虑了材质的膨胀率而设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠也更换完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来谈谈工作的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢之炼金术师阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不放我出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金普利大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只允许钢之炼金术师阁下出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（你就乖乖待在里面）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利的部下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我们一起行动吗 真周到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专程把温莉带来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“强调一切都在我们的掌控之中”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说警戒我们到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要等待机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先遣队带去的食物只能坚持三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过了一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很担心精神方面的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中待一周…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信他们的精神力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法预测在洞穴深处会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我们过了24小时还没回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把洞穴封上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷文中将的事情 是我一个人干的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们什么都没看到 什么都没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果事情暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把一切责任都推在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 北方也变得危险了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 之后得不断取得先机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯是擅长防御的集团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:09:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先发制人是要攻守兼备的军队才做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以和擅长进攻的东方军联合是最佳的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是奥莉薇大人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能选我为合作伙伴很光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥莉薇大人想要的是东方军的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古还是早早消失比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我为了自保
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个情报卖给大总统怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 马斯坦古不是这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来拿 三万五千先士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵妇人 你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代代服侍阿姆斯壮家的卖花婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯 能理解我们并且支持我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是曾经一起战斗过的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 这花怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（那是什么 奇怪的人）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（讨厌 他朝这边看了）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和史密斯的手臂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连金属也被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意 说不定有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨谢尔少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能活下来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他…其他人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则那个就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能有光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子 影子要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇定 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起来吗 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能背多少就背多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜造访非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前来给阁下送紧急文书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能在明天之前过目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我先收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰利姆 还没睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 因为听见大门有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为爸爸回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是霍克爱中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 霍克爱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚了还在工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来给阁下送文书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息时吵醒您 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 杰利姆少爷 该休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则明天要赖床了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是聪明的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 是我们骄傲的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是自己生的孩子 会被说成痴爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是养子所以可以大胆地骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过因为是布拉德雷的远房亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么聪明可能是因为是他的血脉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是夫人的远房亲戚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据大佐说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼年的金格·布拉德雷就被作为实验体抚养
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天涯孤独之身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有什么亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且刚才那个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈喜欢乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的一瞬间感觉到了奇妙的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也在什么地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在清楚地想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫库拉多尼的人造人站在我背后时就是这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰利姆·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个情况下打听我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆子真不小呢 霍克爱中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不拔出你擅长的枪 也是很明智的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法战胜我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和库拉多尼一样是人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 能感觉到库拉多尼无法比拟的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为我和那个家伙是同一等级倒是很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最初的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说是最初的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有一点 也想获得情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想成为我们的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想要棋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无谓的恐吓就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把人质杀了就没有意义了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 霍克爱中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都在你的影子中看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 作为国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统的指示有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是寻找而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处理他是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索和斯卡一起逃亡的马克医生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马克医生和斯卡一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到之后如何处理也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后第三个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在这布里克斯刻下血的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻下血的纹章？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和伊修瓦尔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死人们 在这个土地刻下憎恶和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事怎么做得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连杀人的觉悟都没有就成了军队的走狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不杀人的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不杀人的觉悟？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能贯彻到底 那倒是真理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在理解他们目的的基础上协助他们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看世界变革的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟和觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意志和意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命和生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人和人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界会选择哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果人类被自称进化的人造人毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是历史的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想看着那个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么作为人类 你却要偏袒人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为会让我无所忌惮地使用炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己很异端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果像我这样的人活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说世界选择了像我这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上生命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更有意义的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾 我以为炼金术师都是以自我为中心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我们来谈谈你以自我为中心的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴不得想要用第三只手来获取的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果接受工作的话 就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和阿尔以及温莉谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要和温莉谈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她什么都没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管干什么工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不想因为说谎而背叛她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你不说多余的话 我就同席旁听
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你是人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好 我现在受命作为人类兵器而工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 也许会杀死大量的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种命令拒绝就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 我变成了你们的脚铐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是对自己的天真而生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你们只是想恢复原来的身体而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果参加作战就能得到贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利带着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头的材料是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了 我接受工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先让我搜索斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡杀了温莉的双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 阿尔我也要一起带走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡的人体破坏对他无效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真便利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以大量人的生命为代价做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 哥哥没有打算用那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在从清国的炼丹术里寻找恢复原来身体的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会用炼丹术的女孩似乎和斯卡一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 是装作追踪斯卡 其实是寻找那个女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 估计是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我也得找个像样的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 去最后目击到斯卡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 让我挤一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 再往那边挤一挤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉小姐 请在要塞里等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 刚换了机械铠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有了动作不良就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟去维护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果发生什么 会给洛克贝尔的名字抹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是依旧热心工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作狂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家可是从曾祖父时代开始就很重视工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（我知道 机械宅）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械宅 不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我已经不想再等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒风阵阵的探矿之镇为舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合成兽和人类的总战争不断扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激战的最后迎来的意外结果是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第38话 巴兹库尔的激斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.45,0:24:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在胜利的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人会变得没有防备
